summary:
- Skilled in Psychotherapy (ISTDP-Mindfulness based Therapies)
- Experienced Mindfulness coach 
- Multi style yoga teacher, Yoga Alliance 500RYT;using Yoga as a tool on Health & Wellbeing coaching sessions.
- Strong experience on learning & Development facilitation & management, coaching, designing tailored team development trainings, & leading a diverse team
- Strong experience as an advisor & coach, providing companies and organizations tailormade workshops (Emotional intelligence, Stress management, Mind management,...) for employees & management team
- Experienced in working with migrant & refugees in the area of integration, inclusion and intercultural communication.
- A people person & people manager; People come first...
- Nature, singing, deep communication warm my heart and soul.
- Enjoy reading, watching international films and gardening
- A lifelong learner; Open to new experiences, Open to challenges


Motto; True Communication matters!
